text: Zakhari Sotirov (born 3 January 1973) is a Bulgarian ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1992 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Bulgaria Category:Ski jumpers at the 1992 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
